title: My 10 Books - August 2014 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 2 magazines & 8 books for this month.
There are 5 PDFs & 5 ePUBs. Covers included in separate folder:


01. Encyclopedia of Language Development
02. Mother Queens and Princely Sons - Rogue Madonnas in the Age of Shakespeare
03. My Culture, My Color, My Self - Heritage, Resilience, and Community in the Lives of Young Adults
04. National Geographic Little Kids - July.August 2014
05. Planets & Forecast - September 2014
06. Home Made Simple - Fresh Ideas to Make Your Own
07. Moosewood Restaurant Favorites - The 250 Most-Requested, Naturally Delicious Recipes
08. Outlaws of the Atlantic - Sailors, Pirates, and Motley Crews in the Age of Sail
09. Resistance Band Workbook - Illustrated Step-by-Step Guide to Stretching, Strengthening and Rehabilitative Techniques
10. The Intel Trinity - How Robert Noyce, Gordon Moore, and Andy Grove Built the World's Most Important Company
